---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact MailPilot"
  description="Get in touch with the MailPilot team."
>
  <h1>Contact</h1>
  <p>Have a tool we should review? Found a mistake? Want to pitch a guest post?</p>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@smallmailhub.com">hello@smallmailhub.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>What we respond to</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Corrections to existing reviews (we fix and credit you)</li>
    <li>Suggestions for tools we haven't covered</li>
    <li>Partnership inquiries from affiliate managers</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't respond to</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Sponsored review pitches (we don't do them)</li>
    <li>Link exchange requests</li>
    <li>SEO service sales</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>